description: Actors are seen dressing up according to the film's theme and their character during promotions and that's called 'method dressing'. From the marketing angle of it to the way it creates an impact, ETimes talks to some stylists and marketing experts to analyse this trend!
title: The art of method dressing and its effects!

description: Suryakumar Yadav, the world No.1 T20I batter, shared a humorous moment with teammate Yashasvi Jaiswal on social media as the Indian cricket team prepares for the 2024 ICC T20 World Cup in New York. The team, consisting of Rohit Sharma, head coach Rahul Dravid, and pacer Jasprit Bumrah, arrived in two batches.
title: 'Garden me ghoomega toh...': Surya pokes fun at Jaiswal

description: Prosecutors pleaded with jurors Tuesday to use their "common sense" and find Donald Trump guilty, as the first ever criminal trial of a former president reached its dramatic final phase. The first former or sitting president under criminal indictment, Trump also faces charges in separate cases which include accusations he mishandled classified documents and tried to overthrow the 2020 election.
title: Prosecutor urges jury to convict Trump using 'common sense'

description: In the past decade, experts predicted India would produce a Google or Facebook, but it hasn't happened yet. Global capability centres (GCCs) in India are growing, attracting MNCs. The rise of GCCs is changing cities like Bengaluru, offering vast tech talent and potential for future leaders like Satya Nadella.
title: Will the next Satya Nadella sit out of India?

description: Over the past year of record-shattering warmth, the average person on Earth experienced 26 more days of abnormally high temperatures than they otherwise would have, were it not for human-induced climate change, scientists said Tuesday.
title: ‘Climate change added a month’s worth of extra-hot days last year’

description: Rajasthan continues to face a blistering heat wave with Churu recording a temperature of 50.5 degrees Celsius. Relief is expected with rainfall in Jaipur, Bikaner, and Jodhpur divisions.
title: Churu in Rajasthan sizzles at 50.5C, 3 deaths reported in Jaipur

description: The border district of Ferozepur in Punjab is facing a crisis due to the influx of heroin from Pakistan. Issues like drug abuse, unemployment, and lack of industries are prevalent in the region.
title: Drugs, joblessness and crime: Can ballot bail out Ferozepur?

description: Investigation into child trafficking racket in Hyderabad led to arrest of 8 persons and rescue of 11 children, aged 23 days to 3 years, from Telangana and Andhra Pradesh.
title: 8 held as Hyderabad cops bust child trafficking racket, rescue 11

description: NCW seeks urgent action from DGP Punjab to investigate allegations of inappropriate sexual conduct by AAP Punjab minister Balkar Singh with a 21-year-old woman seeking a job.
title: Punjab mantri's 'sleazy' clip surfaces, NCW seeks probe

description: The White House defines a major ground operation in Rafah, with Israel's actions under scrutiny. President Biden warns against a large-scale military offensive, while the World Court orders a halt to Israel's assault on Rafah.
title: Israel's Rafah operation not a major offensive: US

description: The Indian cricket team has started their preparations in New York for the ICC 2024 T20 World Cup, set to take place in the USA and West Indies from June 2. The first batch of Indian cricketers, including Rohit Sharma, Jasprit Bumrah, Suryakumar Yadav, and head coach Rahul Dravid, have already started their training sessions.
title: Team India begins preparations in New York for T20 World Cup

description: In almost all her political gatherings and rallies, actor Kangana Ranaut, BJP’s candidate from Mandi parliamentary constituency, gets immediately surrounded by fans, who come in droves, pulled by her big screen charisma.
title: Battle Royale? Mandi’s ‘king’ & ‘queen’ spar for supremacy with jibes & insults
